---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Medhat's Blog" description="Learn more about Medhat and this blog.">
  <div class="about-container animate-in">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p>Technical writer, cybersecurity enthusiast, and lifelong learner.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Hey there! I'm <strong>Medhat</strong>, and this is my corner of the internet where I write about 
        the things I learn and find interesting. From cybersecurity deep dives to handy development tools,
        I aim to break down complex topics into clear, digestible posts.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <p>
        This blog focuses on practical, real-world technical topics. Here's what you'll find:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>🔒 Cybersecurity concepts & practices</li>
        <li>🛠️ Developer tools & workflows</li>
        <li>🐧 Linux tips & tricks</li>
        <li>💡 Personal insights & learnings</li>
        <li>📚 Technical tutorials & guides</li>
        <li>🌐 Web development best practices</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
      <p>
        I believe in learning by doing — and writing about it. Every post here is a result of 
        hands-on experience, research, and a desire to share knowledge with others. Whether you're 
        a beginner or an experienced developer, I hope you find something useful here.
      </p>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is built with modern, minimal technology:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>⚡ Astro — Static site generator</li>
        <li>🎨 Vanilla CSS — Custom design system</li>
        <li>🔤 Markdown — Content authoring</li>
        <li>☁️ Netlify — Hosting & serverless functions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Got questions, feedback, or just want to chat? Feel free to reach out on 
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> 
        or <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
